01:02:55,270 --> 01:02:56,556
I'm here to bail out my worker!

537
01:02:57,330 --> 01:03:01,826
- He's been drunk driving. So, he's your worker.
- Yes.

538
01:03:01,826 --> 01:03:04,290
I saw the sign you put up in the community,

539
01:03:04,290 --> 01:03:08,260
encouraging people to quit drinking and drugs.
Don't you ever have your worker read it?

540
01:03:09,250 --> 01:03:11,910
Come on. Help me.

541
01:03:11,910 --> 01:03:14,003
- How much would you like to charge?
- That's enough.

542
01:03:14,608 --> 01:03:16,020
No bail needed now.

543
01:03:16,020 --> 01:03:19,780
I'm sending him to court to settle the fine.

544
01:03:22,110 --> 01:03:23,210
Wit.

545
01:03:23,210 --> 01:03:24,870
Take his fingerprints,

546
01:03:24,870 --> 01:03:26,300
then send them to court.

547
01:03:27,230 --> 01:03:28,230
Yes.

548
01:03:36,510 --> 01:03:37,940
I'll get you.

549
01:03:39,830 --> 01:03:40,830
Please.

550
01:03:42,390 --> 01:03:43,390
Please, sir.

551
01:03:54,630 --> 01:03:56,540
Are you still mad at me?

552
01:03:58,870 --> 01:04:00,460
I'm sorry.

553
01:04:00,990 --> 01:04:04,180
I won't do it again.

554
01:04:04,180 --> 01:04:05,220
I promise.

555
01:04:09,070 --> 01:04:10,860
Is it worth it?

556
01:04:10,860 --> 01:04:16,060
We almost got shut down
and lost our license too.

557
01:04:19,430 --> 01:04:22,380
Ryo, we're the media.

558
01:04:22,380 --> 01:04:26,260
We can't just let the public live
in constant worry like this.

559
01:04:27,030 --> 01:04:30,260
It is our responsibility
to deliver accurate information

560
01:04:30,260 --> 01:04:33,140
- to help people understand better, isn't it?
- Yes.

561
01:04:33,140 --> 01:04:34,176
That's enough.

562
01:04:34,176 --> 01:04:36,630
I know, I studied that as well.

563
01:04:36,630 --> 01:04:43,430
Great. Next up, we'll have a special feature,
a deep academic dive into psychopathy.

564
01:04:44,000 --> 01:04:46,000
I really want to put this one on air, okay?

565
01:04:55,030 --> 01:04:59,260
Hey! No TV broadcast, just online only!

566
01:05:00,110 --> 01:05:01,110
You...

567
01:05:02,300 --> 01:05:07,460
The psychopathic killer leaves a message
on the body to communicate something.

568
01:05:09,150 --> 01:05:10,180
Is it enough?

569
01:05:11,070 --> 01:05:12,980
I think the tone is a little too blunt.

570
01:05:13,590 --> 01:05:16,910
Never mind, I'll connect it
with the previous one.

571
01:05:16,910 --> 01:05:19,190
- Okay, I need another run.
- Alright.

572
01:05:19,190 --> 01:05:20,820
Camera, ready?

573
01:05:20,820 --> 01:05:24,946
Camera and action!

574
01:05:24,946 --> 01:05:30,986
For the latest psychopathic killer,
the symbol left behind was gold leaf.

575
01:05:33,560 --> 01:05:34,560
Hey.

576
01:05:35,270 --> 01:05:36,780
Hey, what's happening?

577
01:05:47,910 --> 01:05:54,340
For the latest psychopathic killer,
the symbol left behind was gold leaf.

578
01:06:03,710 --> 01:06:07,180
The symbol left behind was gold leaf.

579
01:06:10,830 --> 01:06:12,820
The Gold Leaf killer?

580
01:06:34,510 --> 01:06:35,510
Hello.

581
01:06:36,750 --> 01:06:37,750
Doctor.

582
01:06:38,630 --> 01:06:40,580
I believe we should meet.

583
01:06:41,190 --> 01:06:42,190
Sure.

584
01:07:02,270 --> 01:07:04,030
[Chanya]

585
01:07:54,230 --> 01:07:55,230
[Chanya]

586
01:08:27,430 --> 01:08:30,460
I'll go later. Let me get my things first.

587
01:08:30,460 --> 01:08:31,820
Okay, baby.

588
01:08:45,377 --> 01:08:46,730
Hey, PM's son.

589
01:08:46,730 --> 01:08:48,900
Captain, we found a new body.

590
01:09:16,378 --> 01:09:21,150
Gold Leaf was left on the body.
What message is he trying to send?

591
01:09:21,150 --> 01:09:23,020
Or could it be referring to the Five Precepts?

592
01:09:35,823 --> 01:09:38,350
So, in conclusion,
the police won't be able to catch the killer?

593
01:09:38,350 --> 01:09:39,540
- What did you just say?
- No.

594
01:09:40,150 --> 01:09:42,150
I'm getting older every day.

595
01:09:42,150 --> 01:09:45,260
You should have someone
walk with you in the rain.

596
01:09:48,110 --> 01:09:49,540
How do you know?

597
01:09:51,250 --> 01:09:52,900
Your son's still alive.

598
01:09:53,670 --> 01:09:55,860
I know who he is.

599
01:09:57,350 --> 01:09:58,500
I'll kill him.

600
01:10:00,070 --> 01:10:02,140
I told you,

601
01:10:02,140 --> 01:10:05,780
someone like you could never kill anyone.

602
01:10:06,470 --> 01:10:08,246
We'll see.

603
01:10:08,246 --> 01:10:11,110
All five victims knew you.

604
01:10:11,110 --> 01:10:12,940
So you think it was me.
